 Pantera 的 Dimebag 和 Vinnie Paul 的父亲 Jerry Abbott 去世，享年 80 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/jerry-abbott-father-of-panteras-dimebag-and-vinnie-paul-dies-ged-80-3613996?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jerry-abbott- Panteras-dimebag-and-vinnie-paul 的父亲于 80 岁去世Elizabeth AubreyFri, 05 Apr 2024 17:44:18 +0000 Music NewsNews..Metal https://www.nme.com/?p=3613996 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>社交媒体上分享了对雅培的致敬</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jerry-abbott-father-of-panteras-dimebag-and-vinnie-paul-dies-aged-80-3613996">Pantera 的 Dimebag 和 Vinnie Paul 的父亲 Jerry Abbott 去世，享年 80 岁的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pantera">Pantera</a>成员 Dimebag Darrell 和 Vinnie Paul 的父亲 Jerry Abbott 去世，享年 80 岁。</p><p>他去世的消息是由朋友老丹尼·伍德报道的，他在社交媒体上发帖宣布了这一消息。</p><p> “我非常悲伤地告诉大家我的密友杰里·阿博特去世的消息。他昨晚在丹顿的一家护理机构去世。他的家人正在为家人和亲密朋友举行私人葬礼，并计划举行追悼会。很快就会有详细信息。”</p><p> Abbott 是一位音乐家和录音工程师，在 Pantera 的成长过程中发挥了关键作用。他在 80 年代管理乐队并共同制作了他们的专辑。</p><p> 2014年，阿博特出版了自传<i>《Over My Shoulder: The Life and Times of Jerry Abbott》</i> ，在书中他讲述了他与儿子们的关系以及Pantera的成功和随后的解散。</p><p>他在书中写道：“太多的成功会孕育失败，而且经常如此。我认为这是对 Pantera 事件的准确评估。这就像一段美好得令人难以置信的婚姻，接下来你就知道它已经触礁了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3613985" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3613985" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3613985" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Pantera-tribute.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Pantera-tribute.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Pantera-tribute-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Pantera-tribute-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Pantera-tribute-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Pantera-tribute-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Pantera-tribute-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3613985" class="wp-caption-text"> (LR) Pantera 乐队的 Vinnie Paul Abbott、Rita Hane 和 Jerry Abbott 于 2007 年 5 月 17 日在加州好莱坞吉他中心举行的好莱坞摇滚步道颁奖典礼上揭幕了纪念 Pantera 吉他手、已故 Darrell “Dimebag” Abbott 的牌匾– 图片来源：Vince Bucci/Getty Images for VH1 摄</figcaption></figure><p>Dimebag Darrell 的真名是 Darrell Lance Abbott， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/venue-where-dimebag-darrell-was-murdered-is-being-demolished-for-affordable-housing-2964935">他在俄亥俄州的舞台上表演时被一名歌迷谋杀</a>。他的兄弟兼乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vinnie-paul-dead-54-pantera-damageplan-hellyeah-2342836">Vinnie Paul 于 2018 年 6 月因严重冠状动脉疾病突然去世</a>。兄弟俩年龄分别为38岁和54岁。</p><p>去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pantera-celebrate-what-would-have-been-dimebag-darrells-57th-birthday-in-texas-3487370">新改版的 Pantera 在达雷尔 57 岁生日之际向他致敬。</a></p><p>这场悼念活动是在乐队最近在德克萨斯州奥斯汀举行的——这位已故吉他手 1966 年出生于同一个州。</p><p> Pantera <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/surviving-pantera-members-to-reunite-in-2023-for-first-tour-in-20-years-3269542">早在 2022 年 7 月就宣布计划以重组后的阵容重聚</a>，其中包括吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zakk-wylde">Zakk Wylde</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-label-society">Black Label Society</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">Ozzy Osbourne</a> ）、鼓手 Charlie Benante（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anthrax">Anthrax</a> ）、主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phil-anselmo">Phil Anselmo</a>和贝斯手 Rex Brown。</p><p>安塞尔莫最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/phil-anselmo-vinnie-paul-dimebag-darrell-would-want-the-pantera-brand-to-go-on-3549968">在一次新的采访中表示，他认为他已故的乐队成员 Vinnie Paul 和 Dimebag Darrell 会支持乐队目前的重聚。</a></p><p><strong><em>这是一个突发新闻报道——更多内容敬请关注</em></strong></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jerry-abbott-father-of-panteras-dimebag-and-vinnie-paul-dies-aged-80-3613996">Pantera 的 Dimebag 和 Vinnie Paul 的父亲 Jerry Abbott 去世，享年 80 岁的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
奥维尔·派克 (Orville Peck) 与威利·尼尔森 (Willie Nelson) 合作登上《牛仔们经常暗自喜欢彼此》的封面https://www.nme.com/news/music/orville-peck-teams-up-with-willie-nelson-on-cover-of-cowboys-are-frequently-secretly-fond-of-each-other- 3613945?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=orville-peck-teams-up-with-willie-nelson-on-cover-of-cowboys-are-frequent-secret-love-of-otherAnagricel Duran Fri, 05 Apr 2024 16:49:28 +0000 Music NewsNewsCountryLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3613945 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥维尔·佩克和威利·纳尔逊。图片来源：Matt Winkelmeyer 和 Terry Wyatt，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “如今围绕 LGBTQIA+ 群体的言论层出不穷，拥有像威利这样真正的盟友，无所畏惧地自豪地站在我们身边，真是令人鼓舞。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/orville-peck-teams-up-with-willie-nelson-on-cover-of-cowboys-are-frequently-secretly-fond-of-each-other-3613945">奥维尔·佩克 (Orville Peck) 与威利·尼尔森 (Willie Nelson) 合作登上《牛仔们常常秘密地喜欢彼此》(Cowboys Are Overly Secretly Fond Of Each Other) 封面的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥维尔·佩克和威利·纳尔逊。图片来源：Matt Winkelmeyer 和 Terry Wyatt，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Orville-Peck-and-Willie-Nelson.-Credit-Matt-Winkelmeyer-and-Terry-Wyatt-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/orville-peck">奥维尔·派克 (Orville Peck)</a>与乡村传奇人物<a href="/artists/willie-nelson">威利·尼尔森 (Willie Nelson)</a>合作翻唱了内德·萨莱特 (Ned Sublette) 的《牛仔们经常秘密地喜欢彼此》(Cowboys AreFrequently Secretly Fond Of Each Other)。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/orvile-peck-bronco-review-3195236">奥维尔·佩克（Orville Peck）——《野马》评论：蒙面男子以复古乡村的炫目裸露他的灵魂</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲是佩克与华纳唱片公司签约后的首张专辑。 《Cowboys AreFrequently Secretly Fond Of Other》由 Sublette 于 1981 年录制，随后由 Nelson 于 2006 年翻唱。</p><p>佩克在接受<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-country/orville-peck-willie-nelson-dropcowboys-are-frequently-secretly-fond-each-other-1234999336/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》杂志</em></a>采访时谈到这首二重唱时说道：“威利一直在谈论这首歌的主题比以往任何时候都更加重要。他希望它能和我们两个一起开始新的生活。”</p><p>他继续说道：“如今围绕 LGBTQIA+ 群体的言论层出不穷，拥有像威利这样真正的盟友，不害怕自豪地站在我们身边，真是令人鼓舞。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="奥维尔·佩克和威利·纳尔逊 - 牛仔们常常暗自喜欢对方（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BirJMnMcfBs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该二重唱由本·普林斯 (Ben Prince) 执导，随附视频中收录了酷儿男女在酒吧内跳舞和喝酒的片段。佩克和尼尔森在尼尔森幸运牧场的一棵树下唱歌和弹吉他。</p><p>这首歌曲是这位蒙面歌手即将发行的二重唱专辑《Stampede》中的第一首歌曲。 Peck 在 Instagram 上分享了即将发行的 LP 的消息，他写道：“我的二重唱专辑《Stampede》即将推出，其中收录了我的几个好朋友。”</p><p> 《Stampede》将接续 2022 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/orvile-peck-bronco-review-3195236">Bronco</a> 》。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/orvile-peck-bronco-review-3195236">对该专辑的四星评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享道：“这是一幅丰富的风景：完全现代且自豪的酷儿。这是一张毫不掩饰成长的专辑，艺术家沉浸在自己的感情中，但从未陷入自怜。矛盾的是，蒙面牛仔毫无拘束地袒露了自己的灵魂，而且因此而更好。在《Bronco》中，Peck 真实地展现了自己的身份，就像专辑中令人眼花缭乱的复古乡村风格一样。让他骑着马将你带入尘土飞扬的日落之中。”</p><p>佩克还宣布了他的 2024 年北美“Stampede”巡演。查看下面的完整日期列表并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Forville-peck-tickets%2Fartist%2F2532151" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购买门票</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5WHix_x0T7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0